_sText: Just a surf map i put together in my spare time. This is my first surf map, though it is not my first CSS map. Compared to many other surf maps, it is quite small, but I managed to fit a few areas as well as a jail in this map. I would like to thank the FPSBanana community for writing the tutorials that helped me with the creation of this map, a small sampling of which were tutorials about creating weapon dispensers, stripping weapons, and making ramps the right size and angle. Thank you all for helping me with this map.
